  This is a new section to display product information details, it is copied by section main-prodcut.liquid but I did many changes on it.
  1. create a new accordion with name of "Step 1. Add kit to cart" to wrap all ProductInfo. (start at line: 160 and end at line: 552)
  2. create two buttons after the new accordion "Step 1. Add kit to cart" and named them "Step 2. Add your toppings for $5 (50c per serve)(Optional)" 
     and "Step 3. Add reusable accessories(Optional)". (start at line: 554 and end at line: 582)
  3. create a "check out" button. (start at line: 584 and end at line: 590)
  4. create a link (keep browsing) to jump to page of collection/all-collection. (start at line: 592 and end at line: 596)
  5. create javascript to define rules and interactions of Step1&2&3. (start at line: 770 and end at line: 890)
  6. add a checkbox to button Step1 (from line 172 to 179) and add a checkbox for both button Step2&3 (from line 564 to 571) 
  7. create a new css file named: "component-tick-box.css" to define css of checkbox
  8. create javascript to make "Add to Cart" button fixed on the buttom of page if original button "Add to Cart" is invisiable on the page 
     only in mobile version. ( start at line: 894 and end at line: 933)
